from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression 

def predict_stress(steps, calories, heart_rate, minutes, mood): 
    X = [[steps, calories, -1 * heart_rate, minutes] ] 
    model = LinearRegression() 
    model.fit(X, [mood]) ) 
    return int(model.predict(X)[0])
